title: fanoutqa: Who are the top 5 Premier League teams with the most titles, and who are their top scorers along with the total number of goals they have scored in their careers? (770809245b756930)

chat_history.content: Who are the top 5 Premier League teams with the most titles, and who are their top scorers along with the total number of goals they have scored in their careers?

Here are the top 5 Premier League teams with the most titles, along with their top scorers and the total goals scored in their careers:

1. Manchester United (20 titles):
   - Top Scorer: Wayne Rooney - 253 goals

2. Liverpool (19 titles - includes pre-Premier League era):
   - Top Scorer: Ian Rush - 346 goals

3. Arsenal (13 titles - includes pre-Premier League era):
   - Top Scorer: Thierry Henry - 228 goals

4. Everton (9 titles - all pre-Premier League era):
   - Top Scorer: Dixie Dean - 60 goals in the league (383 goals in all competitions)

5. Manchester City (8 titles):
   - Top Scorer: Sergio Agüero - 260 goals

Note: The Premier League era began in the 1992-93 season, so the goal tallies for some players, especially those from Liverpool and Arsenal, are from their entire careers and include goals scored before this era.

functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.
